Package ProjectApplication

Class ProjectApplicationRepository

java.lang.Object
Abstract.Repository<ProjectApplication>
ProjectApplication.ProjectApplicationRepository
public class ProjectApplicationRepository extends Repository<ProjectApplication>
Repository class for managing ProjectApplication entities. Handles operations such as parsing CSV rows, generating headers, and retrieving or deleting applications.
